<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="leave-n">leave <strong><em>n</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /liːv/    美 /liːv/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>休假；假期：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She asked for three days'  leave to take care of her sick son.
她请了3天假照顾生病的儿子。</p></div></div>